description:
Beautiful, Modern and Cozy 2 BR apartment in the heart of Greenwich Village/ Soho. Close to all subway lines and public transportation. apartment has full kitchen, 48" Flat TV Internet, Cable, Wi-Fi, Comfy sofa, Ceiling fans in all rooms, lot of sun light. Lively neighborhood with great night life, tons of Bars, Clubs, Shopping, Restaurants, and Lounges. Next to Washington Square park. Super market and drug stores open 24 hours block away. Bathroom has Jacuzzi tub. No Elevator - It is a wak-up..

Beautifully and tastefully decorated, cozy, and everything you need is there.
Master BR has Queen size bed and Second BR has twin (Murphy) Bed which can be close during day.

Guest will have full access to the apartment, lobby, bike storage area.

I will be available by phone and email. Also, if needed in person, I can arrange someone to help.
